					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4792279#post-3676409</guid>
				<title>Everything You&#039;ve Wanted to Read about SCPs (but were too afraid to ask)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4792279/scp-series-1-tales-edition#post-3676409</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2018 05:12:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Shaggydredlocks</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1722371</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&#8230;and too lazy to search.</p> <p>Well now! We've got ourselves the very beginning of a long-overdue &quot;search Tales by SCP&quot; page!</p> <p>This is open from contributions from the whole community. Instructions and how-to's can be found at the top of the page.</p> <p>Expect the Series 2 and 3 hubs within the next two months.</p> <p>Happy reading, and happy hunting!</p> <p>ETA: Belated credit to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1515889957" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" >mlister</a></span> because holy heck they're putting in a ton of work here.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
